 >After searching the archives, I cannot find a
 >length for the battery cable and ground cable.
 >Anyone know the right lengths.  Any certain brand
 >or kinds of cables that I should get?

 >The positive cable is AWG 4 and 48" long. Most of the replacement cables 
are AWG 6.

For those not in the know, AWG 6 is THINNER than AWG 4. With that length of 
cable, and the current it carries when starting, you want to go thicker if 
you can't get the stock size.

